  "title": "Business Development / Sales Executive",
  "description": "<p>Cleverly SG — a Singapore-grown, digital marketing agency is scaling up its home-base sales team. We’re searching for a sharp <strong>Business Development / Sales Executive</strong> who can turn conversations into long-term partnerships for our SEO, SEM, social-media, content-marketing and AI-chatbot solutions</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<h4>What You’ll Do</h4>\n<ol>\n  <li><strong>Prospect &amp; close</strong><br>\n<em>Source, qualify and convert</em> SMEs and mid-market firms that need performance-driven digital marketing.</li>\n  <li><strong>Consultative selling</strong><br>\nDiagnose pain points, quantify ROI, and craft proposals that map our services to <em>clear business outcomes</em>.</li>\n  <li><strong>Pipeline ownership</strong><br>\nMaintain a healthy funnel in HubSpot, delivering against <em>monthly</em> and <em>quarterly</em> revenue targets.</li>\n  <li><strong>Stakeholder collaboration</strong><br>\nWork hand-in-glove with delivery teams (SEO, Paid, Content, Tech) to ensure seamless onboarding and upsells.</li>\n</ol>\n<p><br></p>\n<h4>Must-Haves</h4>\n<ul>\n  <li><strong>2 + yrs</strong> quota-carrying B2B sales / BD experience (digital agency, MarTech, SaaS or media strongly preferred).</li>\n  <li>Proven track record of <strong>hitting or smashing</strong> targets.</li>\n  <li>Comfort discussing <strong>SEO/SEM metrics</strong> and translating jargon into <em>profit impact</em> for non-marketers.</li>\n  <li>Excellent written &amp; spoken <strong>English</strong>; a plus if you converse in <strong>Mandarin or Bahasa Melayu</strong> with local SMEs.</li>\n  <li><strong>Growth mindset:</strong> self-driven, resilient, keen to learn fast and iterate faster.</li>\n</ul>\n<h4>Nice-to-Haves</h4>\n<ul>\n  <li>Familiarity with <strong>Enterprise Singapore</strong> grants (PSG, SFEC, EDG) and how they shorten sales cycles.</li>\n  <li>Existing network among Singapore’s SME &amp; mid-market community.</li>\n  <li>Experience selling subscription services or retainer-based solutions.</li>\n</ul>",
