    "description": "<p>Cleverly SG is a Singapore-based digital marketing agency established in 2017, offering a comprehensive suite of services including SEO, SEM, social media marketing, web development, and system integration for businesses across various industries. Known for its bold strategies and client-centric approach, the agency has collaborated with notable clients such as Casio, Yale, and Crystal Jade, and is recognized as a pre-approved vendor under Singapore's Productivity Solutions Grant (PSG) program. Cleverly SG emphasizes transparency and strategic thinking to deliver tailored digital solutions that enhance brand visibility and drive business growth</p>",
